ExternalService

An external service allows the ability to add any IP or hostname as a service to be discovered as a service.

Resource Fields

Writeable Fields

Field Type Create Update Default Notes
description string Optional Yes -  
environmentId environment Yes - -  
externalId string Optional - -  
externalIpAddresses array[string] Optional Yes -  
healthCheck instanceHealthCheck Optional - -  
hostname string Optional Yes -  
launchConfig launchConfig Optional - -  
metadata map[json] Optional Yes -  
name string Yes Yes -  
startOnCreate boolean Optional - -  

Read Only Fields

Field Type Notes
data map[json]  
fqdn string  
healthState string  
id int The unique identifier for the externalService
upgrade serviceUpgrade  


Please read more about the common resource fields. These fields are read only and applicable to almost every resource. We have segregated them from the list above.

Actions

activate POST: /v1/projects/${PROJECT_ID}/externalServices/${ID}?action=activate

Input:This action has no inputs

Output: An updated copy of the service resource
cancelrollback POST: /v1/projects/${PROJECT_ID}/externalServices/${ID}?action=cancelrollback

Input:This action has no inputs

Output: An updated copy of the service resource
cancelupgrade POST: /v1/projects/${PROJECT_ID}/externalServices/${ID}?action=cancelupgrade

Input:This action has no inputs

Output: An updated copy of the service resource
deactivate POST: /v1/projects/${PROJECT_ID}/externalServices/${ID}?action=deactivate

Input:This action has no inputs

Output: An updated copy of the service resource
finishupgrade POST: /v1/projects/${PROJECT_ID}/externalServices/${ID}?action=finishupgrade

Input:This action has no inputs

Output: An updated copy of the service resource
rollback POST: /v1/projects/${PROJECT_ID}/externalServices/${ID}?action=rollback

Input:This action has no inputs

Output: An updated copy of the service resource
upgrade POST: /v1/projects/${PROJECT_ID}/externalServices/${ID}?action=upgrade

Input: ServiceUpgrade Field | Type | Required | Default | Notes ---|---|---|---|--- inServiceStrategy | [inServiceUpgradeStrategy](/docs/rancher/v1.6/en/api/v1/api-resources/inServiceUpgradeStrategy/) | No | | toServiceStrategy | [toServiceUpgradeStrategy](/docs/rancher/v1.6/en/api/v1/api-resources/toServiceUpgradeStrategy/) | No | |

Output: An updated copy of the service resource
